I never heard of that, but it reminded me of the sound effects used by Spanish speakers in Spain when talking about eating tasty food, so I was able to guess my way through it.

But I feel your pain (if that is what you are expressing here).

@Paul 

So let me understand this.  You go through all the clues and try to discern the answer without knowing any of the crosses or even the length of the word you need?

That's pretty hard core.

@John White 

